Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.50,0:00:03.16,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Flowing water has no form.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.16,0:00:04.95,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A blowing wind can't be seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.95,0:00:06.46,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}All cases can be freely deduced!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.46,0:00:08.89,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sonoko makes an appearance today after a long absence!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.89,0:00:10.96,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A man and a crime at an ice-skating rink!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.96,0:00:12.62,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.62,0:00:14.55,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.55,0:00:16.47,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.48,0:02:18.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.90,0:02:23.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.45,0:02:27.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.69,0:02:30.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow, take a look at all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:33.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look at all those good-looking men!\NWe've got a big catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.18,0:02:34.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.78,0:02:36.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.60,0:02:41.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko! What about Kyogoku{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.42,0:02:43.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.81,0:02:49.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Makoto{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s more like a wounded samurai than a prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.50,0:02:53.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, he hasn't gotten in touch with me since we went overseas,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.06,0:02:55.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I'm starting to cool on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.75,0:02:59.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Talk like that, and his fangirls will kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.45,0:03:02.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's really popular, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.10,0:03:05.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, well, I'm not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.05,0:03:11.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't just lovingly wait for hubby to return!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.23,0:03:14.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not waiting for Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:19.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My, my. I never even mentioned Shin'ichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.45,0:03:21.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.64,0:03:28.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You chose this skating rink 'cause you two used to play here when you were kids, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:31.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't have any good memories of this place!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.15,0:03:35.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi always made fun of my crummy skating!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.64,0:03:43.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he taught you holding your hands, feet and hips, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.17,0:03:48.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with you, Sonoko?\NWhy are you being so mean today?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.09,0:03:54.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just saying, now's your turn to teach somebody else how to skate!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.98,0:03:56.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's okay. I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.87,0:03:59.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey. Can he skate?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.50,0:04:00.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.98,0:04:03.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've never gone skating with Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.87,0:04:05.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you skate, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.65,0:04:11.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:13.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe this is his first time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.66,0:04:21.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now's my chance to get back at this cheeky brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.45,0:04:23.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop it, Sonoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.37,0:04:25.41,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Oh, that Sonoko...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.11,0:04:29.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.35,0:04:31.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.90,0:04:33.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:40.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Move, move!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:44.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C-Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.15,0:04:44.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.74,0:04:49.24,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Chihiro Itami (27)\NDaughter of a Corporate Executive
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:47.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.15,0:04:51.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:53.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.37,0:04:56.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ow! Help me, Yasuharu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.69,0:04:57.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.04,0:05:00.46,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Yasuharu Misawa (29)\NBanker
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.86,0:05:00.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't skate so fast if you're that clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.46,0:05:02.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:09.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Milk the poor wittle kitten act\Nwhile there's still time, Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.55,0:05:12.52,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Izumi Sano (28)\NOffice Worker
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.94,0:05:15.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once you turn 30, it won't be cute, even coming from a perky little rich girl like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.55,0:05:19.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How come you're always so mean to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.59,0:05:21.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You get on my nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.74,0:05:22.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.88,0:05:26.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on! It's been ages since the clay pigeon shooting club has met!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:27.49,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Yoriko Komatsu (30)\NHousewife
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:28.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's not fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:32.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You do clay pigeon shooting?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.05,0:05:33.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.42,0:05:38.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, that sport where you shoot flying discs with a shotgun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:44.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We did a round this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.13,0:05:47.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a lot more fun with friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:51.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we hadn't met since the accident six months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.30,0:05:54.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Accident six months ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.40,0:05:59.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. You want to hear it, little boy?\NIt's a strange and scary story...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:01.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.02,0:06:06.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How dumb are you? Why tell a kid something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.15,0:06:11.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And I thought I made it clear that I'd go home the minute you said a word about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.15,0:06:11.12,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kunitomo Oda (29)\NFirefighter
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:15.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wow! He's so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:17.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Another samurai type...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.78,0:06:22.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Oda, are you going home?\NI thought we were going drinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.35,0:06:25.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just going out for a smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.37,0:06:29.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Some idiot made me remember something I'd rather not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:32.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.15,0:06:34.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just because he's cute, he thinks he can talk like that to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:38.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you shouldn't have brought it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.57,0:06:40.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It just slipped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.87,0:06:42.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where does he get off calling me an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.70,0:06:44.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the one you guys should be mad at!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.90,0:06:47.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hate that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.51,0:06:52.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's rude, and he's the odd one out...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:54.29,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Odd one out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.29,0:06:58.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you've been saying that for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.32,0:07:00.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.01,0:07:03.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You still haven't figured it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.03,0:07:04.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.87,0:07:07.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.35,0:07:08.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.85,0:07:11.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why's he the odd one out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.77,0:07:15.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way, no way, no way! I can't believe you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.20,0:07:19.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, hurry up and tell us! You're being a pest!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.35,0:07:20.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.68,0:07:23.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the last person I'd tell!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.55,0:07:30.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you'll probably never figure it out,\Nsince you're not a perky little rich girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.41,0:07:31.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.58,0:07:33.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The ladies' room!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.89,0:07:38.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you can't figure it out by the time I get back, I'll drop you a hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:41.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.95,0:07:46.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So how about it, inquisitive Suzuki Financial Group lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.54,0:07:47.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you figured it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.89,0:07:49.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.63,0:07:54.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's getting really crowded here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.55,0:07:56.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're probably here for the fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:59.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah. They do a show every night at 7:00, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.59,0:08:05.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right! From this rink you can see the fireworks go off over the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.85,0:08:08.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, you know about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.59,0:08:10.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're here for that too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.84,0:08:12.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As usual, I'll pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.91,0:08:14.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll just get coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.85,0:08:16.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've seen this show a hundred times!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.70,0:08:20.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you leaving too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.20,0:08:22.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm a little hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:24.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'll be back in time for the fireworks, so wait there!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:27.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:30.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I've had to go to the ladies' room for a while now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.51,0:08:32.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.16,0:08:34.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll be skating here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:38.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If your friends show up,\Nwe'll tell them to gather around.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.84,0:08:40.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure. Sorry for the bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.71,0:08:44.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll be back in a jiffy, so could you do that for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.24,0:08:45.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.58,0:08:53.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! It's already 6:55.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.55,0:09:01.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's taking so long?\NThe fireworks are about to start!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.80,0:09:06.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're not coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:10.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Ran. I need to go to the restroom too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.94,0:09:20.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, you're taking too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.53,0:09:34.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Toilet... toilet...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.75,0:09:37.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.89,0:09:39.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.66,0:09:41.12,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Restroom closed for cleaning. Please\Ncome back later. —\hTropical Land
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.71,0:09:43.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.31,0:09:50.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on a sec!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.40,0:09:54.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a little late to claim the accident was {\i1}my{\i0} fault, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.60,0:10:03.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-Anyway, even if you hide your face like that,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.72,0:10:07.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,people will come running as soon as they hear the shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.56,0:10:10.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll get caught in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.90,0:10:13.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unless—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.27,0:10:20.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.47,0:10:26.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this going to take long?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.95,0:10:30.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:35.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the only restroom you can enter with skates on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.34,0:10:42.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:46.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, the fireworks started!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:48.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, can you see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:49.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For crying out loud.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.36,0:11:07.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.31,0:11:09.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.10,0:11:11.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Especially the ones at the very beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.78,0:11:14.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you changed your mind about watching the show?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.55,0:11:15.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:18.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought it'd be a nice change.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.80,0:11:21.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whew. Made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:25.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought I was gonna miss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.00,0:11:26.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:29.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where's Chihiro and your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.07,0:11:30.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you see them in the restroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.95,0:11:34.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe I missed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.18,0:11:35.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The restroom was being cleaned,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:39.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I changed into my shoes and went to a different one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:43.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, Sonoko's sure taking a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.73,0:11:50.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, that scream just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.25,0:11:52.20,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.95,0:11:54.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.72,0:12:00.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.48,0:12:03.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.83,0:12:10.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened, Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.70,0:12:14.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-O-Over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.44,0:12:35.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.11,0:12:40.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.70,0:13:00.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:06.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.38,0:13:07.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.75,0:13:12.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.58,0:13:15.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't you gonna watch the fireworks?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.13,0:13:16.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.97,0:13:19.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's been a murder! A murder! Mur-der!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.85,0:13:24.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somebody was killed in the restroom near the skating rink!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.38,0:13:30.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone slipped and fell in the restroom near the skating rink?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.25,0:13:32.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.20,0:13:37.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:40.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.61,0:13:42.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.70,0:13:49.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No...{it's there but very faint}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.81,0:13:57.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why Chihiro? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.84,0:14:01.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Police! Out of the way, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.01,0:14:05.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Authorized personnel only! Move aside!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.04,0:14:12.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How ruthless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.39,0:14:13.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.83,0:14:18.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody's been in here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.06,0:14:22.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, when we got here, this boy was inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:27.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C-Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.23,0:14:29.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:35.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just another coincidence!\NSimmer down, Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.22,0:14:37.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't bother with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.99,0:14:39.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.17,0:14:42.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This shotgun looks like the murder weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.92,0:14:48.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's start by determining the owner of this gun from its registration number...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.34,0:14:51.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.01,0:14:53.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the shotgun I use for clay pigeon shooting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.90,0:14:59.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought I put it in a locker with an electronic lock, with all the other guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.73,0:15:01.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Other guns?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.73,0:15:02.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.74,0:15:05.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These three people and I are all members of a shooting club.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.02,0:15:11.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who entered the password for the electronic lock?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.18,0:15:12.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.86,0:15:16.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But everybody knows what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:19.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Last time we were here, we decided to use 9017.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.01,0:15:19.95,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}ku-re-i-na
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.95,0:15:23.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sounds like clay friends in Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.95,0:15:23.69,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}kurē nakama
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.69,0:15:28.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, let's check you four out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.11,0:15:31.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one with gunpowder residue on their body is the killer...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:34.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'll find it on all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.68,0:15:38.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We came here after shooting all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.55,0:15:43.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And maybe the locker just wasn't properly locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.06,0:15:46.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that happened, anyone could've gotten in and—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.83,0:15:48.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that isn't possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:50.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:53.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gun cases for shotguns are required to look like normal bags,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.05,0:15:57.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so people can't figure out what's inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.11,0:16:00.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Izumi's gun case looks like an ordinary leather bag,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:03.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and her shotgun was disassembled.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.50,0:16:06.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only an expert could use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.48,0:16:08.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:12.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the only ones who knew where her shotgun was,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.62,0:16:15.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and could assemble it,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:18.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,were you four, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.81,0:16:20.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.56,0:16:23.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.10,0:16:25.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ask around for any witnesses
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.07,0:16:30.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,who saw a suspicious figure around the lavatory at the time of the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.85,0:16:31.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.79,0:16:33.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.81,0:16:36.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.40,0:16:37.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.48,0:16:41.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw the killer come out of the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:43.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really, Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.93,0:16:50.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a cleaning sign hanging on the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:52.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I kept knocking on the door,\Nbut nobody answered,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.41,0:16:54.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I kept waiting by the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.62,0:16:59.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the fireworks started, so I left the door alone
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.17,0:17:01.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and went to the window to watch with everybody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.60,0:17:03.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And just then...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.60,0:17:08.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw a suspicious person in a hooded coat come out of the restroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:13.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,D-Did you see the person's face?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.18,0:17:16.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. It was hidden behind a hood and a scarf.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:19.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the killer used a coat like that as a disguise
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.66,0:17:22.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and used the sound of the fireworks to hide the gunshot,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:25.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,this is a premeditated crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.40,0:17:31.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll need to question each of you separately.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:36.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd like to know whose idea it was\Nto come to this amusement park.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.09,0:17:37.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.94,0:17:40.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We all decided together!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.13,0:17:44.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now, save it for the interrogation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.10,0:17:45.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, you don't have to bother with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:51.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had a hunch the moment\NI saw the scene of the crime,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.41,0:17:55.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but now that I've heard Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s story, I'm convinced.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.25,0:17:58.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer who shot Itami{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.61,0:18:01.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Izumi Sano{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r},
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.83,0:18:04.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it was {\i1}you{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.05,0:18:07.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, that's not funny! What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.41,0:18:12.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are three things that point to you being the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.08,0:18:16.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, the crime took place in the ladies' room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.52,0:18:19.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer hung the sign on the door\Nto keep other people away,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.07,0:18:23.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then walked in after the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.25,0:18:26.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which means it was a woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.05,0:18:31.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then there's your relationship with the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.58,0:18:37.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been told the two of you\Nfought like cats and dogs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.15,0:18:39.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.95,0:18:42.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That doesn't mean I'd kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.61,0:18:44.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The decisive proof...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.61,0:18:48.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,is the bloodstain left on the wall\Nnext to the corpse's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.99,0:18:50.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bloodstain?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.20,0:18:55.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To you, it might just look like a mark\Nleft by the victim's struggles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.01,0:18:57.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I can clearly see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:19:03.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,as a dying message left by the victim as she passed away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.01,0:19:08.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S for Sano!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:12.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I asked all of your names before\Nthe Inspector came, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.98,0:19:18.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the only one whose name begins\Nwith an S, Sano{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.48,0:19:19.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.66,0:19:20.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think so!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:23.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.95,0:19:26.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As you can tell by examining the body,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.80,0:19:30.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the victim was shot in the chest and died instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.58,0:19:35.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't possible for her to write something with her own blood after she was shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:39.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good point...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.48,0:19:44.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And a man could have called the victim here by telling her one of the women wanted to see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.53,0:19:46.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then he could've entered in disguise.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:51.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then that S is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.22,0:19:52.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.72,0:19:59.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somebody left it there on purpose to incriminate Sano{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.61,0:20:03.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The shotgun is hers too, as you'll recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.44,0:20:06.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this still seems fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.05,0:20:10.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sonoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} knocked on the door just before the crime was committed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.30,0:20:15.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the killer was aiming the gun at the victim and waiting for the fireworks to appear,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:19.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,why didn't the victim scream for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.13,0:20:24.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer was probably hiding in the next stall or something until the fireworks went up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.91,0:20:26.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:29.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's something wet on here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.08,0:20:32.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, on the tip of the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.33,0:20:34.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It's saliva!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.33,0:20:35.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.51,0:20:37.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer pushed the muzzle into the victim's mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.28,0:20:42.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to shut her up until the fireworks started!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.35,0:20:45.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then just as the fireworks went off, the killer lowered the gun to the victim's chest and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.95,0:20:47.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.20,0:20:50.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It couldn't have been any of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.26,0:20:56.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We were all at the skating rink\Nwhen the fireworks started.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.28,0:20:58.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.55,0:20:59.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.55,0:21:01.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were they really there from the start?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:06.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It only takes 30 seconds to get from the restroom to the skating rink.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.13,0:21:11.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when the first firework went off, those three all ran up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.39,0:21:15.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was less than 10 seconds between the first one and the second.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.11,0:21:17.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where were you at that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.58,0:21:23.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was smoking on a bench by the skating rink, with my back to the fireworks.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.29,0:21:26.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only one without an alibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.96,0:21:29.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we've still got no proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.25,0:21:32.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And we don't know his relationship with the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.23,0:21:35.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But at least you know she didn't like the cold, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.95,0:21:37.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.21,0:21:41.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She had her hand in her pocket,\Neven when she was about to be shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.51,0:21:44.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A cellular phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.92,0:21:47.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's nothing on the display.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.65,0:21:50.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She must've been shot before she could call the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.71,0:21:52.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you press redial?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.71,0:21:56.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can find the last person she phoned, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.39,0:21:58.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.15,0:21:59.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.12,0:22:07.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,KIX?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.80,0:22:12.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And 8 pound signs where the phone number usually appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.37,0:22:17.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She probably tried to call for help,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.03,0:22:19.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but was too panicked to dial just by touch.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.68,0:22:21.90,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}KIX...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.99,0:22:25.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}KIX?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.17,0:22:29.30,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait, I've seen this somewhere before...
